The person that never does homework but reminds the teacher about upcoming homework

The nerd

The person who always outsmarts the teacher (usually hates the teacher and tries to prove a point)

The teacher that doesn't let the bell dismiss you

The bully (tries to take your lunch money)

Girls that are obsessed with their phone

The pranksters

Teacher's pet (honestly the one that I hate the most)

The student who gets homeschooled

Mr. Excuses

The rage monster (maybe gets A+ in all of the subjects but gets A- in one of them) I guess the rage monster really wants all perfect grades

Mr. Dirty Locker

The small kid who skips all of his grades just so he can get to college quicker

The person who held back few grades

The homework dumper (he or she dumps homework like he or she doesn't care about it)
